// Destructive organizer-hub acceptance plus a fixed-rate k6 phase. This runs
// only against an explicitly acknowledged disposable Compose project. It owns
// three temporary users, two Docker containers, two Containers rows, and the
// exact semantic audit rows generated by those users; cleanup proves all of
// them are absent before returning.
